title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Airbus H135 helicopter - version 1. 42
description:
The Airbus H135  has been recently update to fix Sim Update 6 issues. After SU 6 the helicopter was stuttering a lot which has now been fixed. In this video we are going to see how if fly's now the fix has been implemented.

The latest version of the helicopter can be downloaded from flightsim.to:
https://flightsim.to/file/8970/airbus-h135-helicopter-project
